profile: Bartlett Tree Experts is a 100+ year old tree and shrub care company with global reach and local roots. We provide science-based solutions, a safety-first record and expert care for your trees and shrubs. Services include pruning, fertilization, insect and disease management and removal. We service the Muskoka area (Bracebridge, Gravenhurst, Bala, PortCarling, Rosseau,lake of Bays)
